description:
Sex, Love and Relationships | Episode 3 | The Spiritual Dimension | Pam Stenzei

The third part of this seminar focuses on the spiritual consequences of sexual intimacy.

Join Pam as she speaks on the spiritual consequences of sexual intimacy in this third part.  Using teachings from Scripture, she discusses the true nature of God and the reasons for his boundaries concerning sex. She also talks of the spiritual alienation bound to occur when we misuse this gift while also offering hope for his redemption.

Teenagers love Pam Stenzel because she tells it to them straight, mincing no words in showing how the pervasive sexual permissiveness of our culture is a deceptive trap. Every young person should have the benefit of the hard-hitting reality check in this four-part series. 

Teenagers have been betrayed! They have not been told the whole truth about the consequences of sexual activity, experimentation and permissiveness. Teenagers love Pam Stenzel because she tells it to them straight, mincing no words in showing how the pervasive sexual permissiveness of our culture is a deceptive trap. Every young person should have the benefit of the hard-hitting reality check in this four-part series. Pam's message is helping thousands avoid disastrous consequences of unwise choices.

Director: Matt Connolly
Starring: Pam Stenzei
